summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Lighting Department; authorizing an exchange of instruments with the One Twenty Four Investment Corporation, a Washington Corporation, and Grace M. Weyand, a single woman, to clarify and release certain encumbrances on property in Section 28, Township 25 North, Range 5 East, W.M. in the vicinity of 124th Avenue Northeast and Bellevue-Redmond Road in Bellevue, Washington.
